  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bca\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc2\u0bb2\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb2\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0ba9\u0bcd, \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0bb5\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0baf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1 - \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Consular Office Closed on Thursdays and Tuesdays - Ministry of Foreign Affairs",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Consular services to the public will be held on Mondays, Wednesdays and Fridays only. The Ministry of Foreign Affairs has announced that it will not be held on Tuesdays and Thursdays.",
        "Due to the prevailing situation in the country, the Consular Affairs Division of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs will provide services to the public only on Mondays, Wednesdays and Fridays from 30 June 2022 to 10 July 2022.",
        "Also applicable to Regional Consular Offices in Jaffna, Matara, Kandy, Trincomalee and Kurunegala.",
        "The public is requested to contact us at the following email addresses for urgent inquiries.",
        "Regional Consular Office - Kurunegala - kurunegala.consular@mfa.gov.lk is mentioned in the statement."
      ],
